spec_data.Name: gkrellm-wifi
spec_data.Description:
Plug-in for gkrellm (a system monitor) which monitors the wireless LAN cards in
your PC and displays a graph of the link quality percentage for each card.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 07 Aug 2017 01:11:03 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Wireless monitor plugin for the GNU Krell Monitors
